rComments: Tough marker and too much homework, but patient and full of responsibility.

Apparently, when you missed more than 2 classes in his class and not being too active in the class discussion (I usually answer homework questions), you got 40-50% for your attendance. Plus, he gives a lot of homework and is very strict. DO NOT take his section if you have a choice!!!
